00:08:22.339 --> 00:08:24.339
Anong ibig mong sabihin?

00:08:24.899 --> 00:08:25.839
Ibig kong sabihin—

00:08:26.660 --> 00:08:28.379
Ako na mismo ang kukuha ng Soul Jade.

